import React, {useEffect, useRef} from 'react'; import {Carousel} from "react-bootstrap"; import {Link} from "react-router-dom"; import * as THREE from "three" import {GLTFLoader} from "three/examples/jsm/loaders/GLTFLoader" const Welcome = () => { useEffect(() => { const scene = new THREE.Scene(); const camera = new THREE.PerspectiveCamera( 75, Number(document.getElementById("place")?.clientWidth) / 500, 0.1, 1000 ); const renderer = new THREE.WebGLRenderer(); renderer.setSize( Number(document.getElementById("place")?.clientWidth), 500 ); const loader = new GLTFLoader(); loader.load( 'scene.gltf', function ( gltf ) { scene.add( gltf.scene ); }); scene.background = new THREE.Color(0xfff) let light = new THREE.HemisphereLight(0xffffff) camera.position.z = 5; function animate() { requestAnimationFrame( animate ); renderer.render( scene, camera ); } let i: any = setInterval(() => { animate(); return clearInterval(i) }, 500) document.getElementById("place")?.appendChild( renderer.domElement ); }, [ ]) return ( <>
